title: Fingerprint Fee Was Received
body: On July 21, 2021, we accepted the fingerprint fee for your Form I-601A, Application for Provisional Unlawful Presence Waiver, Receipt Number YSC2190199000. Our Potomac Service Center location is working on your case. We mailed you a notice describing how we will process your case. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
